\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16253520 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Can you give me your full name?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7497575 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Yes, Louise Henton. Louis}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10122990\charrsid13047356 e}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 . They call me Louie but I always say Louise, it is - I were christened after me grandma.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16253520 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 And your present address is Hillworth Lodge?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7497575 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Lodge, yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16253520 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 You are single?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7497575 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16253520 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 What year were you born?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7497575 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Well I should say it is 1905 isn't it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16253520 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 You're sixty-five now?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7497575 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 I should - no, I'm sixty-five now yes, sorry. I thought - yes, I'm sixty-six in March.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16253520 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 And the place where you were born, was that Leeds?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7497575 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Armley. Outside of Leeds. But we lived at Bramley twenty years when we left t
here owing to dad being on the Corporation there, had the district up there you see, and then we had to come back again to Armley.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16253520 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 How long were you at Armley before you moved?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7497575 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Oh now I couldn't just say, a good while, I was a child, I were only going - to school.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16253520 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Did you move while you were going to school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7497575 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16253520 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 You then went to Bramley?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7497575 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Yes. And we were}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15276634\charrsid13047356  there}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356  twenty years.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16253520 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 And then you went back to Armley.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7497575 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Then we went back to Armley again.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16253520 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Would you say that the bulk of your childhood was}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10122990\charrsid13047356  spent}{\rtlch\fcs1 
\af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356  at Armley?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7497575 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Biggest part of it, yes, Leeds, anyhow, we'll put it down - it's outside of Leeds is Armley.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16253520 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 It's a built up area though is it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7497575 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Yes. I supposed it is, I haven't been since I left - come h
ere. It will be, yes, when I was living, there, yes, it was a main road where we was on.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16253520 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Do you know why it was that you moved?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7497575 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 It was owing to me dad being in Armley district, they gave him Armley you see and he was at Bramley. Well we had to remove owing }{
\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15276634\charrsid13047356 to }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 him being nearer the office in Leeds.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16253520 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Did you have any brothers and sisters?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7497575 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Yes}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15276634\charrsid13047356  I\rquote ve}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356  a }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15276634\charrsid13047356 sis}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 
ter and brother in Leeds. Me brother's two year older - four year older than me. And me sister's two year younger. And me sister's two boys and me brother's none.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16253520 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 How old was your father when you were born?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7497575 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 I don't know how old he was but when he died he was eighty-three.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16253520 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 About how old were you then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7497575 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Well I finished - I left school when I was thirteen, will that be any different to you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16253520 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Do you know how old you were when your father died?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7497575 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 
Died? Oh yes, it's only about - it be - eleven years ago. I thought you meant when he - were at the Corporation, I was going to school when he were - well I was working when he
 was working at the Corporation. I were going to school part of the time and then when I left when I was thirteen I started working and I've worked up 'til being sixty - practically.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16253520 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Do you know where your father came from?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7497575 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Yes. Leicester. But he - that's his home town but he was lodging in Nottingham.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16253520 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Did he then go on to Leeds from there?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7497575 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Yes. When he got married to mother. He was in lodgings at Beeston Hill in Leeds, he was lodging there before he got married to mother.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16253520 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 What was his job?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7497575 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 A gas inspector.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16253520 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Reading the meters?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7497575 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Reading the meters.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16253520 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Did he ever have another job that you know of?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7497575 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Well he was removing before he went on, he was working for Carvers, furniture removers.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16253520 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 That was after he'd finished with the gas works?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7497575 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 No, before - yes, and then he was stoking in a gas house before then.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16253520 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Do you know if he did any casual or part time bobs at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7497575 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Well when he retired he went and worked at the - you know those tablets they mak
e, Yeastvites - he went there, and that was his last job before he died.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16253520 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 What sort of work was he doing there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7497575 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 He was - well I don't know whether he was getting - he was on a machine. Making the tablets I think 'cos he used to bring some home oc
casionally for me.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16253520 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Do you remember him ever being out of work at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7497575 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 No, only when he fell and broke his ribs. He fell and - he was going to the }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid10122990\charrsid13047356 toilet}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356  and he was - he was on the Corporation at the time and he fell and that's the only time I remember him being out of work.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16253520 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Was that for a long time then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7497575 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 About six weeks, that was all. Between six and seven weeks. He's been in St }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid10122990\charrsid13047356 James}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356  you know, St James's. He's been - he had to go - he had an accident and he went out with -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16253520 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 When was this?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7497575 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Before he died.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16253520 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Have you any idea }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10122990\charrsid13047356 how}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356  old your mother was when you were born?
