\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16253520 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 -How old would you be then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7497575 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 
I think I was about - I don't think I was more than fourteen. But - fourteen to fifteen go in for - we were both confirmed together. On a Saturday and the Bishop of Writton came - confirmed us at Bramley.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16253520 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 What did your parents think about swearing?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7497575 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Oh no, you never heard mother - neither me dad - occasionally. But not mother. Oh no, and she hated anybody to swear.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16253520 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 When grown ups were talking could you join in?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7497575 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Yes, if we were there we hadn't - we wasn't sent out when they were talking, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16253520 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10122990\charrsid13047356 Could you}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356  actually join in the conversation?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7497575 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16253520 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 You say you were never punished physically?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7497575 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 On no. Oh no. Me mother never put us in
 a room and said stay there while you - while you - if we'd been naughty, oh no, we'd never - she'd no need to do it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16253520 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Did she have any method of punishing at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7497575 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 No. No. No. She never said if we were naughty or owt, you can't have this, and you won't get a dinner tomorrow or aught }{\rtlch\fcs1 
\af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10122990\charrsid13047356 like}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 - oh no. Oh no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16253520 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 What about your father?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7497575 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 
Never - the same. Oh no. They wouldn't do that to me 'cos we'd been naughty because we never did - we weren't so naughty to do without a meal.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16253520 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Would you say you received the ideas you had about how to behave from both your parents or was one more important than the other?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7497575 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Yes. Both of them. - Grandma included. We was never naughty at front of her.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16253520 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 When you had a birthday how did you celebrate it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7497575 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Mother used to buy us things. Nice things, either clothes or a ring or a bottle of perfume or anything like that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16253520 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Did you have a birthday tea?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7497575 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 A party, yes. And little friends if we wanted. Our own friends. When I was twenty-one I had a beautiful party but I was ill.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16253520 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Can you remember anything you did with your mother or father at Christmas Day?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7497575 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 
Oh yes. We used to have a lovely - we used to have friends come and mother used to buy beautiful presents at Christmas and get us a great bi
g Christmas tree. Put presents on for us and buy us things - I used to love Christmas when I was at home. When I was a child and grown up.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16253520 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 did you have any musical instruments in the home when you were a child?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7497575 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Well - me mother got a gramophone
 - yes, we had a gramophone but it was me brother when he was twenty-one, that's the only think I know. We hadn't a piano or }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10122990\charrsid13047356 owt}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356  like that. We'd a wireless. But me father bought the wireless after mother died - for company.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16253520 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Did anybody in the family sing?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7497575 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Me.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16253520 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 As a child?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7497575 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 
Yes, me. Me sister occasionally. I sung in the Town Hall, I was in the Girls Friendly Society, you know. I had a badge and I lost it before I came here. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10122990\charrsid13047356 
I were there - oh I went for years, we used to go on a Monday night. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Then I went to the Bible class when I finished Sunday school you see, when I got older.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16253520 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Did your parents play any games with you when you were children?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7497575 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Oh yes, mother said, she used to love playing ringa-ringa roses with us and all them sort of games and blind man's buff and - oh yes.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16253520 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Were there books in the house?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7497575 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 
Oh yes, used to buy them little story books when were children. And then when - when we were going to confirm me mother bought us a prayer book to hold.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16253520 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Did you have newspapers and magazines in the house?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7497575 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Yes. Me father used to have the News of the }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10122990\charrsid13047356 World}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 , me mother used to have the Pictorial. And then the evening paper, Evening Post.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16253520 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Do you remember your mother and father reading?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7497575 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16253520 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Both of them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7497575 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16253520 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Did they ever read aloud, either to you or to each other?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7497575 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Yes. they used to read aloud words we didn't know, they'd read it to us.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16253520 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 But not to each other?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7497575 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Each other if they wanted to, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16253520 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 When you were a child do you remember there being a funeral in the family?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7497575 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 
Yes. Well I'm saying when I was a child - me mother lost a little girl and she lost a little - I should have had two - we called her Mary and then - she was expecting a brother older than this w
ould have been that's living now and he died in convulsions. And then after then mother was expecting this sister and the baby was died in the other bad. They called it Mary I think mother said.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16253520 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Do you remember anything about the funeral or not?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7497575 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Oh yes, mother couldn't go to the }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4202748\charrsid13047356 funeral.}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356  I could and me sister went and me brother. And Grandma, I think, father went of course. But she was only a few weeks old. 'Course mother couldn't go 'cos she was expecting this sister you see, the one that's living.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16253520 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Were you children put into mourning?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7497575 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Oh yes. When mother died we was put in -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16253520 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 When the baby died?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7497575 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Oh no, oh no. Me mother really couldn't afford it, I might as well be truthful.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16253520 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 As a child were you taken out it visit neighbours or friends or relations?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7497575 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 
Oh yes. Yes. Yes. I - me father lodged with a friend and we used to go there nearly every Sunday. If they didn't come to our house. Oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16253520 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Were you taken shopping?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7497575 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Yes, taken shopping, taken to Leeds, taken into the park, taken to R}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4202748\charrsid13047356 own}{
\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 
ley Park when it was - what they call Bank Holiday week, to watch all the - you know, what was going on, we - they closed Leeds - when we were in Leeds they closed down for Leeds at Bank Holiday week. And there used to be a - like 
- what do they call it - a celebration in - at Rownley Park and they used to take us to see them dive off the big lake and take us into the - out to tea into the - well there was a - a - cafe in the park or there was a little cottage outside, mother took 
us in there for tea, we used to spend the day up at Rownley Park.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16253520 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Did you ever go out with just your father?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7497575 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Yes. I've - only when mother died. But I have gone out with me dad - oh yes. Oh yes, I used - when he were going out he used to say, whe
re are you going? He used to say, I'm going out. Can I come? Of course you can. Yes. Oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16253520 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 As a child did you ever go away for a holiday?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7497575 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16253520 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Regularly?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7497575 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Not regularly, we've gone - I went with me grandma for a fortnight when I was 
going to school at Bridlington. Just me grandmother alone 'cos mother couldn't leave. You see, she had the others to look after. And then mother had her holiday with my friend's sister when she was grown up, when she was working.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16253520 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 But when you were a child you just went with your grandma?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7497575 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Then, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16253520 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 This one occasion?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7497575 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Yes. I have gone with mother.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16253520 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 When you were a child?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7497575 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Yes. But I've gone with grandma more than mother.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16253520 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Was it usually for a fortnight or a week?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7497575 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Well
 a week, it just depend how much she could afford. We used to save up for our holidays you know, we had a moneybox and put what we got given in and - we wasn't forced to put it in but we did, well then of course mother }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid4202748\charrsid13047356 treated}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356  us as well. Paid the railway fare.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16253520 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Did your brother and sister go as well?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7497575 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 No. Not with me.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16253520 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Did they go on separate holidays?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7497575 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 They went - yes, they - sometimes my sister didn't want to go. Then when we grew up she went with a friend and I went with mine and my br
other went with his young lady of course. When we grew up.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16253520 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 When you went on these holidays with your grandma what sort of things did you do?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7497575 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Ooh, used to go - she used to take me into the park and she used to take me - I could go on the lake - 
on the boats you know, by myself, but she didn't like water and I do. She'd let me go on one of these steam - you know, these boats, steam boats. Then she'd take me to watch the bathing pool and of course I can't }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid4202748\charrsid13047356 swim}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 . I could go paddling if I wanted.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16253520 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 How did you spend your Saturdays when you were a child?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7497575 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 
Oh I could go to the pictures, if I wanted, or I could go to the - to see a pantomime at night if I'd gone to the pictures at afternoon I could go out with mother and a dad at night.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16253520 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 What about Sundays?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7497575 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Sundays the same.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16253520 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Was that taken up with Sunday school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7497575 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Yes, I used to go to Sunday school, then I used to go to church with mother at night and me dad.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16253520 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Did you have different clothes for Sunday?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7497575 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Oh yes. Oh yes, mother was most particular what we wore at weekday we - we wore at weekday and when it was }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4202748\charrsid13047356 Sunday}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 
 clothes we had to keep them while another Sunday. We hadn't to go and change them when we had 'em on at Sunday, oh no. We kept them on all the day and -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16253520 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Did you play games at all on Sundays?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7497575 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Not - no, me mother didn't like us playing games, nor sewing. At Sunday, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16253520 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Did they think it was wrong to work or play on Sunday?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7497575 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Yes. Yes. Me mother didn't even like us sewing at Sunday.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16253520 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 You went to church with your mother?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7497575 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16253520 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Did your father go as well?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7497575 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Yes.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16253520 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Regularly?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7497575 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Not regularly but occasionally.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16253520 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Did your mother go regularly?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7497575 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Oh yes. Me mother used to love to go at Sunday night if she couldn't to at 
morning. In summertime she used to cook dinner at Saturday well she's gone then at Sunday morning with us.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16253520 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 What denomination was it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7497575 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Church of England.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16253520 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Were there any Sunday school outings that you went to?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7497575 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Not then love, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16253520 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 You belonged to the Girls Friendly Society?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7497575 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16253520 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Were there any other social activities at the church?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7497575 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 
We used to go rambles with the church - Girls Friendly Society who - such as where I lived at Ottley, Ottley Chevin and we used to spend a 
day there, take our food with us if we didn't take food we bought it. Mother used to give us money to go with. If we hadn't our own pocket money, but we had our own pocket money then. I was working then.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16253520 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Did the church run any temperance club?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7497575 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16253520 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Was grace said at mealtimes at home?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7497575 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 
It could be but we didn't always - yes, me mother used to say grace but she didn't make a practice of it, you could do - she - we had to be quiet when we said it but we could say it or otherwise not. She liked us to say grace.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16253520 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4202748\charrsid13047356 Were you}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356  taught to say prayers at night?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7497575 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16253520 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Did you have family prayers ever?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7497575 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 No, we just said }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4202748\charrsid13047356 them}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356  at our bedside when we were children, on our own. Mother saw us into bed and then she used to leave us.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16253520 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Did your father take nay interest in politics?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7497575 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 No. Oh - sorry.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16253520 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Do you know what his views were?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7497575 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Labour.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16253520 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 What about your mother?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7497575 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Mother was Labour. And I'm Labour.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16253520 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Do you remember your father and mother voting in an election?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7497575 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Oh yes, I've gone with them.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16253520 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Before 1913?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7497575 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Well I don't know but I've gone with mother and father to vote.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16253520 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 When you were still a child?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7497575 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Yes. And they used to buy us a ribbon when we were children to put in our coat.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16253520 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 In some places people used to feel that they risked losing their job or their house if they voted differently from their employer.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7497575 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16253520 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Do you know whether your father ever felt this?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7497575 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 No, I don't think so. I don't think so, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16253520 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Did he belong to the Labour party?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7497575 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16253520 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Was he an actual member of the party?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7497575 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Yes. And he had - and he went to the Labour club as well.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16253520 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 What about your mother?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7497575 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Mother went with him occasionally and so did I. When I grew up to go to - but w
e didn't drink, well I'm saying we didn't drink, mother'd have a milk stout and - but we didn't go silly with it, we never got drunk, I've never been drunk in me life.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16253520 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Was your mother actually a member of the political party?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7497575 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Oh yes, she wouldn't vote for anything else only Labour.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16253520 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Did they actually take part in the activities?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7497575 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Oh no. Oh no, love, no. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16253520 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 They didn't do any canvassing or anything like that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7497575 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Oh no. Oh no, mother couldn't you see. She'd bad legs, she'd varicose ulcers. Dad'd go but he wasn't asked to go.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16253520 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 How did your mother and father spend their time when they weren't working?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7497575 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 They used to go and sit in the sitting room and read and - we did at Sundays. All go out for a walk at Sunday afternoon. Our
 mother'd take us out for a walk if we wanted to go, if not we used to spend Sunday in - inside in the room.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16253520 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 What about the other evenings, did they sometimes go out?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7497575 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Yes, we've many a time gone on the park, mother's said, are you coming? I've s
aid, yes. Or if I didn't want to go she could leave us in the house, we were quite capable of looking after ourselves.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16253520 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Did your mother have any interests outside the home?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7497575 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Oh yes, she used to love to go - in the park or go away. In the home - oh
 yes, me mother had a day for everything. Wash at Monday and - go upstairs and the Tuesdays and what she didn't finish at Tuesday }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4202748\charrsid13047356 she'd}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356  - finish off at Wednesday, and bake at Thursday and }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4202748\charrsid13047356 clean}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356  on a Friday and -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16253520 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Did she belong to any women's organisations?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7497575 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Oh no. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16253520 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 About what time did your father get home from work in the evenings?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7497575 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Well he got home about five o'clock.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16253520 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 How many evenings a week would he spend at home?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7497575 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4202748\charrsid13047356 Oh He never went out after he'd been working, very, very
 - not during the week, he used to go out at the weekends but not during the week. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Unless mother wanted to go. He used to get his paper and he used to read and -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16253520 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Was it on Saturdays then that they'd go to the Labour club?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7497575 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Me mother never went to
 club with him love. She used to stop with us. Only when - we grew up she'd go with me dad then. But she didn't leave us as children. To go.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16253520 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Did your father go to a pub on his own sometimes?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7497575 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Yes. He has done since mother died. But he -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16253520 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 But when you were a child did he sometimes?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7497575 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Well he did, he's come over - to be truthful, I might as well say, he's come home and me mother's }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid4202748\charrsid13047356 been}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356  vexed with him, he's got over the mark a bit. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4202748\charrsid13047356 But}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356  of course we weren't - we were in bed, we didn't know. And of course what they said - I don't think they ever fell out, they never struck one another if that what you mean. Oh no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16253520 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Did your mother go to the pub as well?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7497575 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 No. Only with me dad when we grew up. But not to leave us.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16253520 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Did your - father or mother belong to any savings club?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7497575 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 No, not as I know of.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16253520 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Not for sickness or anything like that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7497575 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 No. Oh me father used to pay into a thing for me mother when we were }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4202748\charrsid13047356 
working}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 . And then when she couldn't get his pension - her pension while me dad was sixty-five. If that's what you mean.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16253520 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Did your father take part in any sport?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7497575 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Oh no. No, he didn't got football or cricket or wot like that, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16253520 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Did he ever go to the races?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7497575 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Oh yes. He took me to the races once at York, tha
t's the first time I'd ever been to a race. When mother was dead, but not while she was living. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4202748\charrsid13047356 
And when - when we was children me father worked for the Corporation and they had - they was going to have a dinner and a tea in London and me father went, took
 me mother and he spent a week of his holidays, but I didn't go, I've never been to London, and he spent a week with me auntie in London - after the Saturday at the party. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 
He took mother for a holiday and they spent a week there and we stayed with grandma.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16253520 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Did your father ever bet?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7497575 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16253520 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 When you were children?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7497575 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 
Oh not when we were children, I thought you meant recently. Oh yes, he did when grew up, yes, occasionally he'd have a little flutter now and again. Not go to - not to rob the house money, oh no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16253520 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 When you were quite a small child how did you get on which your brother?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7497575 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 All right. We never fell out really.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16253520 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Was there either of them that you felt particularly close to?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7497575 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Well - I was more close to me sister than me brother but I did for - I didn't think more of one nor the other. Oh no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16253520 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Who did you play with as a child?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7497575 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 My sister.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16253520 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Did you play with the neighbours children as well?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7497575 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Oh yes. Oh yes, I had a - a girl called Olive Bottomley and 
then there was Rene Wall - I can think of all the children we used to play with.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16253520 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Where did you play?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7497575 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 In the street. Or in the garden, if we - you know, anywhere. We used to play hide and seek and -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16253520 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Did you play in the other }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4202748\charrsid13047356 children\rquote s}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 ' gardens?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7497575 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Yes, if we wanted to, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16253520 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 What sort of games did you play?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7497575 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Well, we used to play cricket and tennis and - all that sort of a thing. And - hide and seek and blind man's bug and -
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16253520 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 What attitude did your mother adopt if you got dirty while you were playing?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7497575 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 
She never smacked us. No, she'd say, oh dear, have you got dirty again, you'll have to take that off, you do look dirty. Get ready before your dad comes in or get washed before your dad comes in, he will think you're dirty
. But she never smacked us if we got dirty, oh no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16253520 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Could you play with anybody you wanted to?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7497575 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16253520 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Were there any children that your parents would disapprove of you playing with?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7497575 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Oh no. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16253520 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Did you have any particular hobbies like keeping pets or collecting anything?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7497575 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 No. no. Oh I liked the dog, I liked the cat, we both had dogs and cats at home. Me mother was very fond of a dog and a cat.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16253520 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 You say your father went fishing?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7497575 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Yes, he did.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16253520 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Did you go as well?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7497575 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Yes. Mother as well.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16253520 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Did you all go as a family?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7497575 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 
No, when - you see me sister got married and me brother, well there were only mother and I and me at home, well we used to go with me dad fishing then. 'Cos me sister got married.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16253520 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Was this when you were grown up?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7497575 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16253520 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 What about when you were a child?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7497575 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Oh I didn't go fishing then when we were children.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16253520 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Did you go for walks as a child?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7497575 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Oh yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16253520 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 What about bicycling?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7497575 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Oh, I didn't have a bicycle, I had a pram and a doll. Had a }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4202748\charrsid13047356 Sarah}{
\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356  doll, I can think about - and me sister had one, me mother bought us one.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16253520 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Did you have any pocket money when you were small?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7497575 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Ooh yes. Yes. Mother used to give us what she could afford and dad as well. And we got -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16253520 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Was this a regular amount each week?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7497575 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Yes, every weekend. And then we could put so much in the moneybox and then spend the rest.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16253520 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 What did you spend it on?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7497575 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 On sweets.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16253520 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Did anybody outside the home help your mother to look after the house ever?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7497575 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16253520 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 As a child your grandmother was living with }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4202748\charrsid13047356 you}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 ?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7497575 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16253520 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 If your mother was ill or confined to bed how did she manage then, was it your grandmother?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7497575 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 I looked after her and her mother did. When I was grown up.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16253520 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 When you were still a child if your mother was ill was it your grandmother who looked after her?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7497575 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Grandma looked after her, yes. And me dad.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16253520 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 What happened when your younger sister was born, was it your grandma who was looking after you then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7497575 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16253520 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Were there any other relatives living nearby?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7497575 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16253520 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Did your parents have friends?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7497575 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Me moth-r - no, me mother hadn't any friends. Only - on me father's side, me father - me aunties and that. But she }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4202748\charrsid13047356 hadn\rquote t}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356  - didn't go o
ut with her friends. No, only me sister when she grew up, she went out with her, her mother. They went out regularly together to }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4202748\charrsid13047356 Morecambe}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 .
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16253520 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 So your parents didn't have any friends around?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7497575 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16253520 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 What about neighbours?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7497575 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Well she spoke to the neighbours but she wouldn't have them in talk - calling as they call it. She never did like that me mother. No.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16253520 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Did your parents ever go out visiting friends or relations?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7497575 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Oh yes. Oh yes. But they took us with them when they went, they never left us at home by ourselves.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16253520 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Was it mainly relations they went to?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7497575 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Yes. That's right. And then that friend that me dad lodged with before he was married, he used to go.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16253520 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 People say that in those days they used to make their own amusements.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7497575 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Yes. We did.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16253520 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 What do you think your parents did when they were together with their friends and relations?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7497575 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Well they used to talk and - as far as I know, but we weren't there you see, we were in bed.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16253520 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Do you think they might have played games?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7497575 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4202748\charrsid13047356 Well me father used to play dominoes with us and - tiddly winks and - cards.}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16253520 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 But with other adult people?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7497575 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Oh yes, when he were - but they didn't come in the house but when he went away on holiday they used to play.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16253520 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Many people divide society into different social classes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7497575 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16253520 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 In the time before 1918, when you were still a child, did you think of some people belonging to one social class and others to another?

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7497575 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 No, I don't - can't say I }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4202748\charrsid13047356 did}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 , no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16253520 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Were there some people who you thought were more important in the district than others?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7497575 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Well I did, yes. I thought - I don't know who to say but I always used to think that someone was very standoffish to what we were.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16253520 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 What sort of people would these be?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7497575 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Well I suppose them at belonging to a club or better off people.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16253520 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Were you ever brought up to treat people of one sort differently from another?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7497575 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Oh yes. Oh yes. We couldn't cheek anybody. Mother wouldn't let us cheek anyone.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16253520 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Was there anybody that you had to be specially polite to, anybody that you had to call sir or madam?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7497575 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 
Oh no. But when me auntie came she didn't like us to be naughty or ought like that. She was a trained nurse, had two aunties trained nurses in London.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16253520 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 What about people like the clergy?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7497575 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Well they'd come to us - mother, if she was ill, or if he was in the district he'd come in and see mother.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16253520 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 What sort of people would he associate with as his friends do you think?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7497575 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Oh I didn't - I don't think he made any more than he did - working class people.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16253520 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 What about the teachers, did they make friends with people?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7497575 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Our teachers, schoolteachers? Yes, they - used to come and see mother if we were - you know - if we were - well we weren't nau
ghty, she never had to come and see mother 'cos we weren't naughty at school. No.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16253520 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 But did they make friends with people?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7497575 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Oh yes. Oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16253520 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Any sort of people?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7497575 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16253520 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Or any particular sorts of people?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7497575 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 No. They'd talk to anyone. In a proper way, not anybody.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16253520 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 What about shopkeepers?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7497575 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Yes, she always had a word with them when she went shopping.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16253520 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 What sort of people would the shopkeepers?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7497575 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Oh very nice. They were very nice to mother.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16253520 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 And who would they associate with do you think?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7497575 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Well I don't know really.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16253520 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 What about farmers, would there be any farmers round your way?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7497575 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Oh yes, I used to go out with a young woman that had a farm at the G.F.S., her father and mother kept a farm and they wou
ld - they would let me go down there, but I were grown up then, I were in the Girls Friendly Society. But not as a child. They called then }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4202748\charrsid13047356 Norfolk\rquote s}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 . Kept the farm at Bramley.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16253520 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 What about employers, do you know if there were any employers living in the }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid4202748\charrsid13047356 Armley}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356  district of Leeds?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7497575 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Not as I know - oh yes, but I don't know who they were, mother didn't associate with them nor dad.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16253520 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 And you never came into contact with them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7497575 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16253520 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Have you any idea if there was any difference between the
 sort of people who went to the Church of England and those who would go to chapel?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7497575 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Oh no, me mother made 'em both the same and I did. I didn't think I was better than they were and mother didn't.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16253520 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 But do you }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4202748\charrsid13047356 think}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356  there was any difference in the sort of people?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7497575 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16253520 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Was the congregation at the church better off financially than the people at the chapel?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7497575 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 No. No, I didn't - we didn't think so, no. We didn't -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16253520 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Would there be a typical cross section?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7497575 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 No, no, one didn't think more than the other, no, I know what you mean, oh no, we were all sociable.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16253520 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 In the are where you }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4202748\charrsid13047356 lived}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356  did all the people of the same sort of class as yourself have the same standard of living?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7497575 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 No. Some didn't like going to church. Some didn'
t like going to chapel. But mother didn't make any difference, she didn't say you should go or ought like that, oh no, she let them just please theirself.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16253520 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 What about their standard of living, would everybody in the same district as you have the same sort of standard?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7497575 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Yes, that's right, oh yes. Were all very nice.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16253520 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Would there be some families that you'd regard as rough?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7497575 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Yes. Yes. Some that didn't care whether they wear - Sunday clothes for weekdays or not if that's what you mean. But we
 were made to keep ours for Sunday and what we wore - had for weekday we keep for weekdays.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16253520 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Was there any particularly rough family that you knew of?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7497575 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 No, not as I know of, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16253520 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Do you remember a distinction being felt between craftsmen and labourers?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7497575 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16253520 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Do you think your mother say herself as belonging to a particular social class?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7497575 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 No I don't think so, no.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16253520 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Was it possible at that time to move from one class to another, to get better off or something like that and start
 moving with people in a different class of society?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7497575 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 
No. No. She didn't bother. If she got where there was a - a neighbour that was better off than herself she didn't think herself any better than her, no. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16253520 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Do you remember any body being described as a real lady or a real gentleman?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7497575 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 What me mother used to associate with? All me aunties were better off than us, that's all I know of.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16253520 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 But was there anybody in the district that you heard referred to as a real gentleman?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7497575 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Oh yes, bu
t he had a business. If that's what you mean love. Do you mean that? Yes, oh they was in business, yes. 'Cos the little girl I played with at school, her father was in a rope business, but she didn't think herself any better than my mother, if that's what
 you mean.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16253520 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Do you remember seeing a policeman around where you lived as a child?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7497575 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Oh yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16253520 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 What did you think of him?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7497575 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 I wasn't frightened. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16253520 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 How did he treat people?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7497575 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Who - the policeman? He used to speak to us, good mor
ning and good afternoon and - have you been naughty? I used to say, no, not as I know of.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16253520 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Was your home rented or did it belong to you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7497575 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Rented. No, it didn't belong to us, it was rented.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16253520 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Did you see anything of your landlord?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7497575 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Oh yes, he come every week.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16253520 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 What did you think about him as a landlord?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7497575 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 
Oh all right, yes. We had one a gentleman and one a lady when we were at Armley. But when we were at Bramley it was a gentleman but at Armley it was a lady, were two sisters, the house we went in what I've just left - spoke about.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16253520 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 But your first house was a man?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7497575 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16253520 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 He was a good landlord was he?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7497575 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Yes. He used to do the repairs, oh yes. In reason.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16253520 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Do you remember feeling that your parents had a struggle to make ends meet?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7497575 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 
Yes, they had at one time. Mother had to go out to work, wash and clean. Yes. For a lady that she knew and she kept a shop, she had to go out - cleaning and washing, 'cos dad hadn't a big wage. When we was little. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16253520 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 And your grandma looked after you while she was out?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7497575 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16253520 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 What did you feel about it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7497575 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Well I thought it was a shame she had to go.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16253520 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 What difference did it make to the family when your father was out of work?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7497575 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 He wasn't out of work.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16253520 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 But when he had that }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4202748\charrsid13047356 period}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356  off ill?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7497575 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Well it didn't make any difference to me - when he broke his ribs - it didn't make any difference to the housekeeping. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16253520 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Did you ever have to get financial help from any source?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7497575 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Not as I know of. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16253520 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 How old were you when you first went to school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7497575 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 
I should be - probably five, I don't know, four or five but the - or probably six, they didn't go I think at that time while they were six year old. I don't think while I was six. But they can g
o at five but I don't think they'd have us then while we were six.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16253520 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Before you went to school did you have any lessons from anybody?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7497575 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Mother used to teach us to read. And sew. And - you know, show us how to do that. Then she'd recite to us.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16253520 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Before you went to school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7497575 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16253520 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 When you first started school what time of the morning did you go?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7497575 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Nine o'clock. 'Til four.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16253520 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 You went all day?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7497575 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16253520 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 What kind of a school was it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7497575 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 National school. A board school.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16253520 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Was it a mixed school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7497575 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Yes, boys and girls. More girls than boys.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16253520 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 How did you get there, id d it take you long?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7497575 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 No, could only - we walked from home. We had -'t to take a bus or ought.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16253520 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 It only took you a few minutes did it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7497575 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16253520 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Did anybody go with you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7497575 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 
No. mother'd see us in but there was no need because she thought we were capable of looking after ourselves. Grandma used to take me sister 'cos she didn't like going to school, if that's what you mean. But I used to - I'
ve been at school when grandma's brought her. Brought her to school. I went on me own.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16253520 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 You went home for your dinner?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7497575 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Yes. And tea.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16253520 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 What did you think of school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7497575 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Very nice. I was quite happy at school.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16253520 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 What did you feel about your teachers?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7497575 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Oh could get on with them all right. Never was caned at school. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16253520 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Did the teachers emphasise certain things like manners or tidiness?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7497575 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Oh yes. And I'll tell you what the }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4202748\charrsid13047356 headmistress}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 , and I was rather - I didn't care for it - when she told us about womanhood. The headmistress. She told us how we - when we got older what things meant and - that was the headmistress. About womanhood.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16253520 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 About how old would you be when you got that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7497575 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Well - to be truthful - just before I left school she told us about it. And she was a Miss, I forget what they call her now.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16253520 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Did they emphasise punctuality?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7497575 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Oh yes, we hadn't to be late.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16253520 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 What about ways of speaking?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7497575 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 No, they liked us to be very - they didn't like to hear us talk rough or anything like that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16253520 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 You say you weren't punished at school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7497575 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Not as - no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16253520 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 How did the teachers punish children?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7497575 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Well if they was naughty they used to just tap them and put them at back of the blackboard.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16253520 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Were the girls treated the same as the boys?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7497575 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16253520 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 What sort of offences did they have to commit to do that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7497575 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 To do that, well we'll say that we was doing sums and they pushed you and - you know, I can do a }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid4202748\charrsid13047356 sum}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356  better than you and they didn't like it 
and they wanted us to - and used to copy over on to our sum book. And then if they were naughty and pushed us - they'd keep them in school longer than us and - or put them in the blackboard and stay there while we left at four o'clock. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15276634\charrsid13047356 Then}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356  treat them - talk to them afterwards.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16253520 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Did your parents show an interest in your }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4202748\charrsid13047356 schoolwork}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 ?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7497575 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16253520 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Did they used to ask you what you did?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7497575 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 What we did at school, what have you been doing today, and so and so. I used to say - of course when I was yo
ung we used to play - well they play in sand now but we didn't then, we just played games while we got into a higher school.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16253520 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Did your parents visit the school - and meet the teachers?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7497575 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Oh yes. Yes, they used to come and see mother did teachers fr
om weekday school. More so if we - not just because we were poorly with being at home, they used to like to talk to mother. My mother.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16253520 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Did the other children come from similar types of home to your own?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7497575 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 I think so, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16253520 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Did the teachers single out some children for different treatment?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7497575 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Oh no. She used to treat us all pretty all alike.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16253520 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Were there any gangs or groups in the school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7497575 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Oh no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16253520 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Were there any children who seemed to be left out of things?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7497575 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 No, I can't say they did, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16253520 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Did you go on to another school from that one?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7497575 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 No, I left from there the National school.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16253520 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 You were at the one school all the time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7497575 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 All the time.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16253520 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 How old were you when you left?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7497575 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Thirteen. I went into cookery. At school. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4202748\charrsid13047356 Baking}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 .
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16253520 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 While you were still at school?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7497575 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 While at school, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16253520 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Would you have stayed on longer if you'd had the opportunity?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7497575 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 If me mother and father had been better off to let us go to high school, yes. But they weren't you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16253520 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Did you attend any part time classes after you left school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7497575 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 No. Only night school, yes, I'm sorry. Yes, I used to go to night school.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16253520 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 What did you go for?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7497575 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Well we used to do - sewing and talks and - and - this - I used to make those raffia baskets. Fancy work. Crafts, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16253520 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Do you have any regrets about your education?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7497575 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 No. Can't say I do, I was quite happy at school.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16253520 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Do you think you benefited from attending school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7497575 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16253520 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 While you were still at school did you ever have a part time job to earn a little extra money?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7497575 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 No. Oh no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16253520 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 What was your first full time job?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7497575 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 I went into the printing - at Tatham Toothills at Bramley. In the glueing.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16253520 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 In a printing works?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7497575 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16253520 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 How did you get that job?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7497575 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Well I had to - I had to walk it from Bramley, down - Station Lane they called it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16253520 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 How did you get the job?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7497575 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 How did I get it? From the Labour Exchange. From - oh they sent me from school to the Labour Exchange to get it.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16253520 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 And what exactly did you have to do?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7497575 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 I was in the glueing. Doing bookbinding.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16253520 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 What hours did you work?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7497575 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Eight to five I think it was.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16253520 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Was that from Monday to Friday?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7497575 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16253520 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 What about Saturdays?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7497575 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 We didn't work Saturdays then. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16253520 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 You didn't have a half day?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7497575 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 No. No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16253520 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 You worked Monday to Friday, eight 'til five?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7497575 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Yes. Yes. That was that, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16253520 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Did you have any holidays with pay?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7497575 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16253520 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 With pay?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7497575 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16253520 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Right from when you first started?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7497575 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 
Yes. Yes, 'cos I went into - yes - oh not when I first started work, no, sorry, I thought you meant - I was there about - oh - I think I were there about six month before I got a - a pay - a holiday with pay. Oh no, twelve month before I g
ot full pay when I had a holiday, I'm sorry. I was there - had to work twelve months before I - got a holiday with pay. Then I -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16253520 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 How long a holiday did you get then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7497575 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 A fortnight.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16253520 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 In your first job can you remember what you were paid?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7497575 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 I }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15276634\charrsid13047356 can\rquote t}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356  love, no. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16253520 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 You can't remember what your first wage was?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7497575 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Oh yes. When I worked at - eight shillings.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16253520 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 As things were in those days did you feel that that was a fair wage or not?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7497575 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 No I didn't.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16253520 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Did you give any of the money to your mother?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7497575 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 I give it all. And then she gave me back pocket money.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16253520 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 What was it spent on, did it go in the family budget?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7497575 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16253520 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 How much did you get back?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7497575 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Two shillings.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16253520 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 You got a fair proportion of it back?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7497575 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Yes. And then I used to put so much in a box and so much I spent.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16253520 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Did you have to buy your own clothes out of that two shillings?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7497575 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Oh no. Oh no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16253520 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Your mother bought them?
