\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4202748\charrsid13047356 Tatham}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356  Toothills. Oh no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16253520 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 How did you get on with the other people who worked there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7497575 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 All right.
