I liked it very much. I should have been there - me sister could have been made forewomen at the same place I worked at. But she went after me.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16253520 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 What dates would you be working at this firm, from about 1918 would it be?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7497575 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Be - yes, it would be, yes. 'Cos I left when I were thirteen and I left at the Thursdays as it was Good Friday on the Friday.
