\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7497575 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 Yes. Numbering the pieces. Then I went on billing and mending.
