a
king. So her son, his - his left - his wife had left him and the little girl they had to put in a home, little Linda. Anyhow, she - I went over a weekend and talked it over with her and she said she wouldn't go if I didn't go. Anyhow I went with her and I
've removed twice. We went to - we got a flat at Bramley but she didn't stay.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16253520 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 You were a sort of housekeeper companion?
