 there.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16253520 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356 You've had quite a varied }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4202748\charrsid13047356 career}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
