}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4202748\charrsid13047356  before}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15616576\charrsid13047356  the vo}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4202748\charrsid13047356 t}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
